Summary:&#xC2;&#xA0;BRC will work with movement partners to support the NSD of the Somalia Red Crescent. Support will include BRC funding, technical expertise, problem-solving and a seconded NSD specialist to the ICRC Somalia delegation. This project aims to incrementally increase the impact of the NS&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s operations and sustainability.&#xC2;&#xA0;&#xC2;&#xA0;


PNSs/Partners:&#xC2;&#xA0;Somali RC, ICRC, IFRC, Norwegian RC&#xC2;&#xA0;&#xC2;</narrative>
